/* ========== 비교 함수 ========== */
// 날짜 정규화: "2026-04-21", "2026.4.21", "2026.04.21" → "20260421"
function normDate(s){
  if(!s) return '';
  const m = String(s).match(/(\d{4})[년.\-\/\s]*(\d{1,2})[월.\-\/\s]*(\d{1,2})/);
  if(!m) return cleanStr(s);
  return m[1]+m[2].padStart(2,'0')+m[3].padStart(2,'0');
}

function cmpText(label, v1, v2, n1, n2){
  const a=cleanStr(v1), b=cleanStr(v2);
  if(!a&&!b) return mkCI('info','i',label,'양쪽 모두 미기재','');
  if(!a&&b) return mkCI('pass','✓',label,'폼 미입력 (증빙값 참고)',mkDiff([{tag:n2,val:v2,cls:'s2'}]));
  if(a&&!b) return mkCI('info','i',label,n2+' 미첨부/미기재',mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:v1}]));
  // 날짜 형식 비교 (포맷 차이 허용)
  const d1=normDate(v1), d2=normDate(v2);
  const isDate = d1.length===8 && /^\d{8}$/.test(d1);
  const ok = isDate ? (d1===d2) : (a.includes(b)||b.includes(a));
  if(!ok) globalErrors++;
  return mkCI(ok?'pass':'fail',ok?'✓':'✕',label,ok?'일치 ✓':'불일치 ⚠',mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:v1},{tag:n2,val:v2,cls:'s2'}]));
}

function cmpAmt(label, v1, v2, n1, n2, tol=0){
  if(v1===null||v1===undefined||v1===''){
    if(v2===null||v2===undefined||v2===0) return mkCI('info','i',label,'양쪽 모두 값 없음','');
    globalErrors++;
    return mkCI('fail','✕',label,'폼 입력 누락 ⚠',mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:'미입력'},{tag:n2,val:fmtAmt(v2),cls:'s2'}]));
  }
  if(v2===null||v2===undefined||isNaN(v2)||v2===0) return mkCI('info','i',label,n2+' 내역 없음',mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:fmtAmt(v1)}]));
  const a=Number(v1), b=Number(v2);
  let isOk=Math.abs(a-b)<=tol;
  let vatNote='';
  if(!isOk){
    if(Math.abs(Math.round(a*1.1)-b)<=tol){isOk=true;vatNote=' (VAT포함=✓)';}
    else if(Math.abs(Math.round(b*1.1)-a)<=tol){isOk=true;vatNote=' (VAT별도=✓)';}
  }
  if(!isOk) globalErrors++;
  return mkCI(isOk?'pass':'fail',isOk?'✓':'✕',label,
    isOk?'금액 일치 ✓'+vatNote:'오차범위 초과 ⚠ (차이: '+fmtAmt(Math.abs(a-b))+')',
    mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:fmtAmt(a)},{tag:n2,val:fmtAmt(b),cls:'s2'}]));
}

// VAT 호환 비교 (매절용)
function cmpAmtVAT(label, v1, v2, n1, n2){
  if(v1===null||v1===undefined||v1==='') return cmpAmt(label,v1,v2,n1,n2,0);
  if(v2===null||v2===undefined||isNaN(v2)||v2===0) return mkCI('info','i',label,n2+' 내역 없음',mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:fmtAmt(v1)}]));
  const a=Number(v1),b=Number(v2);
  let ok=Math.abs(a-b)<=1, note='';
  if(!ok&&Math.abs(Math.round(a*1.1)-b)<=1){ok=true;note=' (VAT포함)';}
  if(!ok&&Math.abs(Math.round(b*1.1)-a)<=1){ok=true;note=' (VAT별도)';}
  if(!ok) globalErrors++;
  return mkCI(ok?'pass':'fail',ok?'✓':'✕',label,
    ok?'일치 ✓'+note:'불일치 ⚠ (차이: '+fmtAmt(Math.abs(a-b))+')',
    mkDiff([{tag:n1,val:fmtAmt(a)},{tag:n2,val:fmtAmt(b),cls:'s2'}]));
}

function mkCI(cls,icon,label,det,diffHtml){
  return `<div class="ci ${cls}"><div class="cs">${icon}</div><div class="cc"><div class="cl-lbl">${label}</div><div class="cl-det">${det}</div>${diffHtml}</div></div>`;
}
function mkDiff(items){
  if(!items.length) return '';
  return '<div class="diff">'+items.map(i=>`<div class="dr"><span class="dtag ${i.cls||''}">${i.tag}</span><span class="dval">${i.val}</span></div>`).join('')+'</div>';
}

